title: Crash day track - Stunt Extreme
description:
Hi everyone i made a track for Crashday game and i want to share it! :atari:

Its called Stunt extreme!
BEST TRACK FOR STUNT SHOW!!!
U can do a race too!




Readme:


How to setup:

1. Unzip the files
2. U will have the choise between Stunt extreme stunt and Stunt extreme race.
When u want to race, you use the race version and if you want to do stunt shown, use the stunt version.
3. Now go to program file ---> Atari ---> Crashday ---> trkdata ---> tracks
(Or just copy this: C:Program FilesAtariCrashdaytrkdatatracks).
Then move all data to that map.

***WARNING*** U CAN CHOOSE BETWEEN RACE VERSION AND STUNT VERSION DO NOT MOVE THE MAP TOO BUT ONLY THE FILES IN IT!
(With extension *.trk, *.tga *.tex).

Now launch Crashday.
Then choose your gametype.
And search for a track with name Stunt extreme (Or for race Stunt extreme race).
Choose your car, and --------------------- ENJOY!!!
